[{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0109","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0109.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-6218","title":"RARLAB WinRAR 目录穿越远程代码执行漏洞","description":"WinRAR 在处理压缩包内文件路径时存在目录穿越漏洞，攻击者可构造包含特殊路径（如 \"../\"）的恶意压缩包文件并诱导用户打开，触发缓冲区溢出导致远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 WinRAR 多个版本，无需身份认证但需用户交互配合，CVSS 评分 7.8，危害等级高。用户应升级至最新版本或应用官方补丁修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-2025-6218"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-06-21T01:15:29.123","updated":"2026-06-17T10:01:24.380","remediation":"立即升级 WinRAR 至 7.12 或更高版本（建议升级至最新版 7.23），该漏洞已在 7.12 版本中修复。无法立即升级时，避免打开来源不明的压缩文件，并禁用 WinRAR 自动解压功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.win-rar.com/singlenewsview.html?&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=276&cHash=388885bd3908a40726f535c026f94eb6","https://www.zerodayinitiative.com/advisories/ZDI-25-409/","https://foresiet.com/blog/apt-c-08-winrar-directory-traversal-exploit/","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2025-6218","https://www.secpod.com/blog/archive-terror-dissecting-the-winrar-cve-2025-6218-exploit-apt-c-08s-stealth-move/","https://github.com/Chrxstxqn/CVE-2025-6218-WinRAR-RCE-POC","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-6218.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/f8a21b0c30953d5926478bb080c200645e84a23a/2025/CVE-2025-6218.json","https://github.com/lal0ne/vulnerability/blob/5b9f397c1970203b1764fb7a66a0ffac39bef4cc/WinRAR/CVE-2025-6218/README.md","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/a7fcebc1b9e9a88d443be844dae279be54e22ef4/data/2025/CVE-2025-6218-ignis-sec_CVE-2025-6218.md","https://github.com/gelusus/wxvl/blob/0190a57b50c784bda47a3b9ac049eaf5bb577d6e/doc/2025-07/%E3%80%90%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E5%A4%8D%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%91WinRAR%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-2025-6218).md","https://github.com/skimask1690/CVE-2025-6218-POC/blob/84713c2fd25c644c8ae3aaa59897bf0a56dd3236/CVE-2025-6218.bat","https://github.com/4ESTSEC/wxvl/blob/26b15b25c2543f872c330110db4ab2967c7c33e0/doc/2025-07/CVE-2025-6218%20Poc%E5%A4%8D%E7%8E%B0%E5%8F%8A1Day%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2025/6xxx/CVE-2025-6218.json","https://github.com/Neo23x0/signature-base/blob/43b2b2faafdaeb7f00102673f62555a2feb04c1b/yara/exploit_rar_archive_with_path_traversal_aug25.yar","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/aaa966adf56b88bf2eba7f47ee24a777c6208719/2025/CVE-2025-6218/crear_rar_malicioso.bat","https://github.com/skimask1690/CVE-2025-6218-POC","https://github.com/absholi7ly/CVE-2025-6218-WinRAR-Directory-Traversal-RCE","https://github.com/speinador/CVE-2025-6218_WinRAR","https://github.com/ignis-sec/CVE-2025-6218","https://github.com/mulwareX/CVE-2025-6218-POC","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-6218"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0109.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0108","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0108.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-5777","title":"Citrix NetScaler ADC/Gateway 内存信息泄露漏洞","description":"Citrix NetScaler ADC 和 Gateway 的认证接口存在输入验证不足漏洞，当设备配置为 Gateway（VPN 虚拟服务器、ICA 代理、CVPN、RDP 代理）或 AAA 虚拟服务器时，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向 `/p/u/doAuthentication.do` 端点发送特制 HTTP 请求触发内存越界读取，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Citrix NetScaler ADC 和 Gateway 14.1 等多个版本，CVSS 评分 9.3，危害等级严重。厂商已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-2025-5777"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-06-17T13:15:21.523","updated":"2026-06-17T09:48:43.670","remediation":"立即将受影响 NetScaler ADC/Gateway 升级至 14.1-43.56 或 13.1-58.32 及以上版本（FIPS/NDcPP 版本请联系 Citrix 支持获取对应修复版本）。升级后执行 `kill sessions` 命令清除已有会话，防止攻击者利用已窃取的内存数据持续访问。该漏洞无临时缓解措施，无法通过 WAF 签名或防火墙规则规避，必须升级修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://support.citrix.com/support-home/kbsearch/article?articleNumber=CTX693420","https://citrixbleed.com","https:/