/0190a57b50c784bda47a3b9ac049eaf5bb577d6e/doc/2025-07/CVE-2025-5777%EF%BD%9CCitrix%20NetScaler%20ADC%E5%92%8CNetScaler%20Gateway%E5%86%85%E5%AD%98%E6%B3%84%E6%BC%8F%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%EF%BC%88POC%EF%BC%89.md","https://github.com/cloudflare/cloudflare-docs/blob/368e16ffd3e2fe129ba5fa6b7b6c4ffb42daf854/src/content/changelog/waf/2025-07-21-waf-release.mdx","https://github.com/Shivshantp/CVE-2025-5777-TrendMicro-ApexCentral-RCE/blob/d9523daccc0ce0cbb0c0feb911d4fef2dd1aab05/cve-2025-5777-poc.py","https://github.com/fox-it/citrix-netscaler-triage","https://github.com/win3zz/CVE-2025-5777","https://github.com/bughuntar/CVE-2025-5777","https://github.com/mingshenhk/CitrixBleed-2-CVE-2025-5777-PoC-","https://github.com/Chocapikk/CVE-2025-5777","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-5777"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2025/POC-AVE-2025-0108.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0108.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0037","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0037.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-5349","title":"Citrix NetScaler ADC 及 NetScaler Gateway 管理接口访问控制不当漏洞","description":"NetScaler ADC 和 NetScaler Gateway 的管理接口存在不正确的访问控制漏洞（CWE-1284），具有网络访问权限的攻击者可利用 NetScaler 管理接口的权限验证缺陷，绕过访问限制获取未授权访问。该漏洞影响运行特定固件版本的 NetScaler ADC 与 NetScaler Gateway 设备，可能导致敏感信息泄露或系统配置被篡改，CVSS 评分 8.7，危害等级高。Citrix 已发布安全公告并建议用户尽快升级修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.7,"aliases":["CVE-2025-5349"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-06-17T13:15:21.377","updated":"2026-06-17T09:47:44.240","remediation":"升级 NetScaler ADC / Gateway 至以下安全版本：ADC 及 Gateway 14.1 升级至 14.1-43.56 及以上，13.1 升级至 13.1-58.32 及以上；ADC FIPS 12.1 升级至 12.1-55.328，13.1 升级至 13.1-37.235；ADC NDcPP 13.1 升级至 13.1-37.235。如无法立即升级，可在网络层面限制仅可信管理网段访问 NetScaler 管理接口（Management Interface），并启用 IP 白名单或防火墙规则阻断非授权来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://support.citrix.com/support-home/kbsearch/article?articleNumber=CTX693420","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-5349.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/f8a21b0c30953d5926478bb080c200645e84a23a/2025/CVE-2025-5349.json","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/a7fcebc1b9e9a88d443be844dae279be54e22ef4/data/2025/CVE-2025-5349-olimpiofreitas_CVE-2025-5349-Scanner.md","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/aaa966adf56b88bf2eba7f47ee24a777c6208719/2025/CVE-2025-5349/README.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2025/5xxx/CVE-2025-5349.json","https://github.com/TonneauBenjamin/ANSSI_Project/blob/f0e2d5e8be75f0351e759642d04d728399b4faa9/data/raw/first/CVE-2025-5349","https://github.com/adysec/hwpoc/blob/7f9d328c5fbc6b96e5e86ea6c9dab85e4e384533/docs/2025/citrix_cve-2025-5349.toml","https://github.com/sec-dojo-com/cve-poc/blob/0d273a0b2821f58c8dfa9e9b4a2ad049f300e8ec/pocs/2025/CVE-2025-5349.md","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/7614318c7ea4c24f707447d3fff16042945e6e08/2025/5xxx/CVE-2025-5349.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2025/06/GHSA-927h-58v2-fqv5/GHSA-927h-58v2-fqv5.json","https://github.com/olimpiofreitas/CVE-2025-5349-Scanner","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-5349"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2025/POC-AVE-2025-0037.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2025/EXP-AVE-2025-0037.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0037.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0025","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0025.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-47165","title":"Microsoft Excel 释放后使用远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Excel 2024 存在释放后使用（Use-After-Free，CWE-416）内存破坏漏洞。当用户打开攻击者精心构造的恶意 Excel 文档时，程序在处理特定对象时未能正确管理内存生命周期，导致已释放内存被再次访问，未经身份认证的远程攻击者借此可在受害者系统上执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Excel 2024 及相关 Office 套件版本，攻击需诱使用户打开特制文件，本地触发代码执行，CVSS 评分为 7.8（高危）。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-2025-47165"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-06-10T17:23:36.527","updated":"2026-06-17T09:27:32.213","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 官方发布的 CVE-2025-47165 安全更新补丁，可通过 Windows Update 自动获取或访问 Microsoft Update Catalog 手动下载安装。如暂时无法安装补丁，建议在受影响的 Office 应用中禁用宏执行，并启用受保护视图以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://msrc.microsoft.com/update-guide/vulnerability/CVE-2025-47165","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/52343","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-47165.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/2025/47xxx/CVE-2025-47165.json","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/57b2f46f8b4a48cfba3cb8b60306b43a8ab2b242/2025/47xxx/CVE-2025-47165.json","https://github.com/imSkows/Cyber-Vulnerability-Analysis-Data/blob/db26c44c5f45c25514223a46675daec7eea03092/data/first/CVE-2025-47165","https://github.com/0xMarcio/cve/blob/3b956963db597dfc3808b14bb6c1e0feecc70f0a/2025/CVE-2025-47165.md","https://github.com/adysec/hwpoc/blob/e2c3d33b7e2870449a687c9b1cfa4c48990c946b/docs/2025/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF_microsoft-excel-2024%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-cve-2025-47165.toml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2025/06/GHSA-29gg-qvj7-46c7/GHSA-29gg-qvj7-46c7.json","https://github.com/TonneauBenjamin/ANSSI_Project/blob/f0e2d5e8be75f0351e759642d04d728399b4faa9/data/raw/mitre/CVE-2025-47165","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/2025/CVE-2025-47165.json","https://github.com/gelusus/wxvl/blob/0190a57b50c784bda47a3b9ac049eaf5bb577d6e/doc/2025-06/%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A66%E4%B8%AA%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%EF%BC%81%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%832025%E5%B9%B46%E6%9C%88%E8%A1%A5%E4%B8%81%E6%97%A5%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%80%9A%E5%91%8A.md","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-47165"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0025.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0077","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0077.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-33073","title":"Microsoft Windows SMB 客户端特权提升漏洞","description":"Windows SMB 客户端存在访问控制不当漏洞（CWE-284），已获得授权的攻击者可通过构造恶意 SMB 服务器诱导目标客户端连接，利用 SMB 协议对访问权限的验证不充分的缺陷实现权限提升，进而可能实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 Windows 11 等版本，CVSS 评分 8.8，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.8,"aliases":["CVE-2025-33073"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-06-10T17:23:02.967","updated":"2026-06-17T09:13:04.220","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 2025 年 6 月安全更新，各版本修复版本号分别为：Windows 10 1507 升级至 10.0.10240.21034、Windows 10 1607/Server 2016 升级至 10.0.14393.8148、Windows 10 1809/Server 2019 升级至 10.0.17763.7434、Windows 10 21H2 升级至 10.0.19044.5965、Windows 10 22H2 升级至 10.0.19045.5965、Windows 11 22H2 升级至 10.0.22621.5472、Windows 11 23H2 升级至 10.0.22631.5472、Windows 11 24H2 升级至 10.0.26100.4349、Server 2022 升级至 10.0.20348.3745。亦可启用 Windows Update 自动获取修复。临时缓解措施：在防火墙及边界路由器上阻止 TCP 139/445 端口的入站 SMB 流量，并限制 SMB 仅对受信任网络开放。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://msrc.microsoft.com/update-guide/vulnerability/CVE-2025-33073","https://www.vicarius.io/vsociety/posts/cve-2025-33073-detection-script-improper-access-control-in-windows-smb-affects-microsoft-products","https://www.vicarius.io/vsociety/posts/cve-2025-33073-mitigation-script-improper-access-control-in-windows-smb-affects-microsoft-products","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2025-33073","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/52330","https://github.com/matejsmycka/CVE-2025-33073-checker","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f13