 REST API 安全过滤器仅匹配 `/rest` 及其子路径，未正确处理带文件扩展名的请求（如 `/rest.html`），导致攻击者可通过在 REST API 路径后添加扩展名绕过默认安全限制，访问 REST API 索引页面，从而泄露已安装扩展信息。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，无需认证即可远程利用，影响 GeoServer 2.26.3 之前版本及 2.25.6 之前版本。官方已在 2.26.3 和 2.25.6 版本中修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.3,"aliases":["CVE-2025-27505"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-06-10T15:15:23.903","updated":"2026-06-17T09:03:43.363","remediation":"升级 GeoServer 至 2.26.3 或 2.25.6 及以上版本。若无法升级，修改 ${GEOSERVER_DATA_DIR}/security/config.xml，将 rest 过滤器路径改为 /rest.*,/rest/**，将 gwc 过滤器路径改为 /gwc/rest.*,/gwc/rest/**，然后重启 GeoServer 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/geoserver/geoserver/pull/8170","https://github.com/geoserver/geoserver/security/advisories/GHSA-h86g-x8mm-78m5","https://osgeo-org.atlassian.net/browse/GEOS-11664","https://osgeo-org.atlassian.net/browse/GEOS-11776","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-27505.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-27505.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/010b0aa4fab18a47a1dfa699acc027ecfea23b55/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-27505.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/2025/27xxx/CVE-2025-27505.json","https://github.com/SourByte05/Vulnerability-Wiki-PoC/blob/887b19465e0912159dcc21abb385b73dcbc283ba/2025/GeoServer-CVE-2025-27505-%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%B3%84%E9%9C%B2/GeoServer-CVE-2025-27505-%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%B3%84%E9%9C%B2.md","https://github.com/selinuxG/Golin/blob/6354d5fac23ae8d582cb7616fdd290d9deeee5cf/poc/yaml-poc/poc-yaml-GeoServer-CVE-2025-27505.yaml","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2025/CVE-2025-27505.rules","https://github.com/iris-sast/iris/blob/3a12f45750f58135bcc58c7fdf4c20786b600e31/data/Dockerfiles/geoserver_CVE-2025-27505_2.26.2/157/Dockerfile","https://github.com/hack007x/veil_poc/blob/5cfe1da6e975ba816d728597885a5c5e79bda8bd/cves/2025/CVE-2025-27505.poc","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/94ba69fdac5ced9eb8795ce09aa042cbb168d31b/2025/27xxx/CVE-2025-27505.json","https://github.com/adysec/hwpoc/blob/e2c3d33b7e2870449a687c9b1cfa4c48990c946b/docs/2025/geoserver_geoserver-rest-api-%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%AA%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-cve-2025-27505.toml","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-27505"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2025/POC-AVE-2025-0014.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0014.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0029","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0029.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-49002","title":"飞致云 DataEase Postgresql JDBC 绕过远程代码执行漏洞","description":"飞致云 DataEase 是一款开源商业智能与数据可视化工具。在 2.10.10 之前的版本中，此前针对 CVE-2025-32966 的修复补丁存在缺陷：由于该补丁仅以区分大小写的方式禁止 JDBC 连接串中的 INIT 与 RUNSCRIPT 关键字，攻击者可通过大小写变换（如 Init、runsCRIPT 等）绕过该限制。在具备数据源校验接口（如 /de2api/datasource/validate）访问权限的前提下，攻击者能构造特制的 PostgreSQL JDBC 连接参数，借助 INIT/RUNSCRIPT 执行任意 SQL 或系统命令，从而实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响所有低于 v2.10.10 的 DataEase 版本，CVSS 评分为 8.2（高危），官方已在 2.10.10 版本中修复，暂无其他可用的临时缓解措施。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.2,"aliases":["CVE-2025-49002"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-06-03T21:15:22.550","updated":"2026-06-17T09:30:39.097","remediation":"建议立即将飞致云 DataEase 升级至 v2.10.10 及以上版本，该版本修复了针对 CVE-2025-32966 补丁的绕过问题（因大小写不敏感导致 INIT 和 RUNSCRIPT 被绕过）。升级前可在网络层临时限制对 /de2api/datasource/validate 接口的访问来源，仅允许可信管理网段访问，并关闭公网暴露的数据源校验接口以降低被利用风险。官方未提供其他可用缓解措施，请务必尽快完成版本升级。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/dataease/dataease/security/advisories/GHSA-999m-jv2p-5h34","https://github.com/dataease/dataease/security/advisories/GHSA-h7hj-4j78-cvc7","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-49002.yaml","https://git