outputTokens\":30,\"totalTokens\":16746}}","description":"飞致云 DataEase 是一款开源商业智能与数据可视化工具，其 2.10.10 之前版本存在 JWT 认证绕过漏洞。由于密钥验证机制未能正确生效，攻击者可伪造任意 JWT 令牌绕过身份认证，进而通过 PostgreSQL JDBC 接口实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响范围广泛，攻击复杂度低，无需用户交互，CVSS 评分 7.7，危害等级高。厂商已在 v2.10.10 版本中修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.7,"aliases":["CVE-2025-49001"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-06-03T21:15:22.410","updated":"2026-06-17T09:30:38.973","remediation":"将 DataEase 升级至 v2.10.10 或更高版本，修复 JWT 认证绕过漏洞。如无法立即升级，可通过防火墙限制 DataEase API 接口访问，并部署 WAF 规则过滤伪造 JWT Token 的恶意请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/dataease/dataease/security/advisories/GHSA-xx2m-gmwg-mf3r","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-49001.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-49001.md","https://github.com/vulhub/vulhub/blob/f7944fe38a3988ee533761e6cdb5e68d67eefff2/dataease/CVE-2025-49001/README.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/d09fb918849614ec417315b66ba20a16a39f16a4/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-49001.yaml","https://github.com/Threekiii/Awesome-POC/blob/0f9e22b660cb1ea12c1c3668f9128d93e08da412/Web%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E/DataEase%20JWT%20%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%20CVE-2025-49001.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/2025/49xxx/CVE-2025-49001.json","https://github.com/Threekiii/Vulnerability-Wiki/blob/b32b83c01eabac4d6b4b334852be9cff76ba67ee/docs-base/docs/webapp/DataEase-JWT-%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-CVE-2025-49001.md","https://github.com/gelusus/wxvl/blob/0190a57b50c784bda47a3b9ac049eaf5bb577d6e/doc/2025-06/%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E9%A2%84%E8%AD%A6%20%20DataEase%20JWT%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%EF%BC%88CVE-2025-49001%EF%BC%89.md","https://github.com/wooluo/nuclei-templates-2025hw/blob/37e9617426e2a