-01 或 v12.0.0+security-01 及以上版本。如无法立即升级，可禁用匿名访问并在反向代理层限制对 /public/ 路径的路径遍历请求，同时确保 Content-Security-Policy 中 connect-src 指令生效以阻止 XSS 利用。若未使用 Grafana Image Renderer 插件，建议卸载以降低 SSRF 风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://grafana.com/blog/2025/05/23/grafana-security-release-medium-and-high-severity-security-fixes-for-cve-2025-4123-and-cve-2025-3580/","https://grafana.com/security/security-advisories/cve-2025-4123/","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/52491","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-4123.yaml","https://github.com/ItsNee/Grafana-CVE-2025-4123-POC","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-4123.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/f8a21b0c30953d5926478bb080c200645e84a23a/2025/CVE-2025-4123.json","https://github.com/eeeeeeeeee-code/POC/blob/11c00cc5e129cb7d6ed8a99ef1fc108ae83719b8/wpoc/Grafana/Grafana%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%AA%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83SSRF%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-2025-4123).md","https://github.com/zan8in/afrog/blob/2f4b82909698139f3589d577b113dd4e51dc5c96/pocs/afrog-pocs/CVE/2025/CVE-2025-4123.yaml","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/0f1885b9ad0c36bab067e4e3d61739350d154cdf/data/2025/CVE-2025-4123-kk12-30_CVE-2025-4123.md","https://github.com/gelusus/wxvl/blob/0190a57b50c784bda47a3b9ac049eaf5bb577d6e/doc/2025-06/CVE-2025-4123%EF%BC%9AGrafana%20%E4%B8%AD%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E9%87%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E7%9A%84%20XSS.md","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2025/CVE-2025-4123.rules","https://github.com/canonical/ubuntu-security-notices/blob/c8de6f2665da1a2cdd26202c7512bf4fd032dd66/osv/cve/2025/UBUNTU-CVE-2025-4123.json","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/aaa966adf56b88bf2eba7f47ee24a777c6208719/2025/CVE-2025-4123/readme.md","https://github.com/Simpsonpt/AppSecEzine/blob/5f446fcfcccf21c49b6f4258aeb7ced58439d410/Ezines/589%20-%20AppSec%20Ezine","https://github.com/NightBloodZ/CVE-2025-4123","https://github.com/ynsmroztas/CVE-2025-4123-Exploit-Tool-Grafana-","https://github.com/punitdarji/Grafana-cve-2025-4123","https://github.com/MorphyKutay/CVE-2025-4123-Exploit","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-4123"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0021.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0024","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0024.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-4679","title":"群晖 Active Backup for Microsoft 365 密钥信息泄露漏洞","description":"群晖 Active Backup for Microsoft 365（ABM）存在凭据泄露漏洞。在 ABM 安装配置过程中，群晖中间件服务 SynoOauth（synooauth.synology.com）在处理 OAuth 授权码回调时，会在 HTTP 302 响应的 Location 头中以明文形式泄露 ABM 全局应用注册的 OAuth client_secret。该密钥属于群晖在其自身 Microsoft 租户中注册的 ABM 多租户应用程序的全局凭据，攻击者仅需观察一次中间件的 HTTP 响应即可获取该密钥。利用泄露的 client_id（b4f234da-3a1a-4f4d-a058-23ed08928904）和 client_secret，攻击者可通过 OAuth 客户端凭证授权流程在任意已部署 ABM 的组织 Microsoft 租户中获取访问令牌，进而以应用权限（Group.Read.All、ChannelMessage.Read.All）读取该租户内所有 Teams 频道消息、群组信息及 Outlook 数据，造成跨组织数据泄露。该漏洞影响所有使用 ABM 的组织，安装量超过 120 万，攻击者无需目标租户内的任何权限即可实施利用，危害范围覆盖不同安全边界。Synology 已在服务端修复此问题，用户无需采取额外措施。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.5,"aliases":["CVE-2025-4679"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-05-16T09:15:18.257","updated":"2026-06-17T09:33:46.653","remediation":"Synology 已在服务端修复该漏洞（旋转了 Active Backup for Microsoft 365 的全局 OAuth 客户端密钥），ABM 作为云托管服务无需用户在 DSM 端执行任何操作。建议用户前往 Microsoft Entra 管理中心审查\"Synology Active Backup for M365\"企业应用程序权限，确认是否仍需保留 Group.Read.All 和 ChannelMessage.Read.All 等高权限，如不再使用 ABM 则移除该服务主体；同时检查 Entra 登录日志中来自 ABM 客户端 ID（b4f234da-3a1a-4f4d-a058-23ed08928904）的异常调用记录，并监控 Microsoft Graph API 活动日志以排查未经授权的 Teams 频道消息和群组数据访问行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.synology.com/en-global/security/advisory/Synology_SA_25_06","https://modzero.com/en/blog/when-backups-open-backdoors-synology-active-backup-m365/","https://modzero.com/static/MZ-25-02_modzero_Synology-Active-Backup-M365.pdf","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-4679.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/f8a21b0c30953d5926478bb080c200645e84a23a/2025/CVE-2025-4679.json","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/0f1885b9ad0c36bab067e4e3d61739350d154cdf/data/2025/CVE-2025-4679-fevar54_CVE-2025-4679-SecureOAuth-Demo---Enfoque-educativo.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/2025/4xxx/CVE-2025-4679.json","https://github.com/imSkows/Cyber-Vulnerability-Analysis-Data/blob/db26c44c5f45c25514223a46675daec7eea03092/data/mitre/CVE-2025-4679","https://github.com/sec-dojo-com/cve-poc/blob/0d273a0b2821f58c8dfa9e9b4a2ad049f300e8ec/pocs/2025/CVE-2025-4679.md","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/d2626315618f92c3b6f631256244cb094cbffa68/2025/4xxx/CVE-2025-4679.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2025/05/GHSA-544f-g2r6-4rv9/GHSA-544f-g2r6-4rv9.json","https://github.com/TonneauBenjamin/ANSSI_Project/blob/f0e2d5e8be75f0351e759642d04d728399b4faa9/data/raw/first/CVE-2025-4679","https://github.com/kidrek/VigilIntel/blob/cfb2327d8869eaaa4d885703b23a3735545da14f/2025/06/2025-06-30-report.md","https://github.com/fevar54/CVE-2025-4679-SecureOAuth-Demo---Enfoque-educativo","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-4679"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0024.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0026","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0026.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-47423","title":"Personal Weather Station Dashboard 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Personal Weather Station Dashboard 12_lts 版本存在路径遍历漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向 /others/_test.php 发送特制的 test 参数（如 ../../../apache/conf/ssl.key/server.key）实现目录遍历，从而读取服务器任意文件，包括以明文方式泄露服务端 SSL 私钥等敏感信息。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 5.8，危害等级中危。建议升级至最新版本修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.8,"aliases":["CVE-2025-47423"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-05-07T18:15:43.393","updated":"2026-06-17T09:28:06.057","remediation":"升级 PWS Dashboard 至 12_lts 之后的安全版本；如无补丁，立即删除或禁用 `/others/_test.php` 文件；在 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）层面添加规则，拦截包含 `../` 的 `test` 参数请求；限制 Web 进程对敏感目录（如 `/etc`、SSL 密钥目录）的读取权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/haluka92/CVE-2025-47423","https://pwsdashboard.com/","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-47423.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-47423.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/f8a21b0c30953d5926478bb080c200645e84a23a/2025/CVE-2025-47423.json","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/010b0aa4fab18a47a1dfa699acc027ecfea23b55/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-47423.yaml","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/a7fcebc1b9e9a88d443be844dae279be54e22ef4/data/2025/CVE-2025-47423-Haluka92_CVE-2025-47423.md","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/aaa966adf56b88bf2eba7f47ee24a777c6208719/2025/CVE-2025-47423/README.md","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2025/CVE-2025-47423.rules","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/2025/47xxx/CVE-2025-47423.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/a2f3ff3fa5db5c7705ebd942909ec114df063700/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2025-47423.yaml","https://github.com/adysec/hwpoc/blob/333a12945888842887b9d7f35a124feef86df7c3/docs/2025/pws_pws-dashboard-%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-cve-2025-47423.toml","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/57b2f46f8b4a48cfba3cb8b60306b43a8ab2b242/2025/47xxx/CVE-2025-47423.json","https://github.com/Haluka92/CVE-2025-47423","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-47423"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0026.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0006","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0006.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-46719","title":"Open WebUI 存储型跨站脚本漏洞","description":"Open WebUI 是一个自托管的人工智能平台，在 0.6.6 版本之前存在存储型跨站脚本漏洞。攻击者可在聊天消息中插入未转义的 HTML 标签和恶意 JavaScript 代码，当其他用户打开包含恶意代码的聊天记录时，脚本会在受害者浏览器中执行，窃取访问令牌从而完全控制受害者账户。若受害者是管理员，攻击者可进一步创建恶意 Python 函数实现服务器端远程代码执行。此外，该漏洞可通过社区共享功能实现跨用户传播，危害范围广泛。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.4,"aliases":["CVE-2025-46719","GHSA-9f4f-jv96-8766"],"sources":["ghsa"],"published":"2025-05-05T19:15:57.197","updated":"2026-06-17T09:26:52.230","remediation":"立即升级 Open WebUI 至 v0.6.6 或以上版本，该版本已对 HTML 标签进行正确转义以防御 XSS。如无法立即升级，建议在管理面板中关闭「Enable Community Sharing」功能，并禁止用户分享聊天记录以降低攻击面。临时缓解措施还可配置 WAF 规则过滤聊天消息中的恶意 HTML/JavaScript 载荷。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/open-webui/open-webui/blob/main/src/lib/components/chat/Messages/Markdown/MarkdownTokens.svelte#L269-L279","https://github.com/open-webui/open-webui/commit/6fd082d55ffaf6eb226efdeebc7155e3693d2d01","https://github.com/open-webui/open-webui/security/advisories/GHSA-9f4f-jv96-8766","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2025/CVE-2025-46719.md","https://github.com/Tencent/AI-Infra-Guard/blob/e00b340019f3b31282b4417e15c49f027f0909d3/data/vuln/openwebui/CVE-2025-46719.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/928db9679b69032a137f1c2f3374c28367145ef0/cves/2025/46xxx/CVE-2025-46719.json","https://github.com/Tabll/gemnasium-db/blob/c78813392a686be9ed8245543249abb80331d014/pypi/open-webui/CVE-2025-46719.yml","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/90bd0a835ff7ed8cfea0a199ea9e2f05e33d6c81/2025/46xxx/CVE-2025-46719.json","https://github.com/sec-dojo-com/cve-poc/blob/b705b33e466c706c1129370e07ab2e4166c35b4c/pocs/2025/CVE-2025-46719.md","https://github.com/pypa/advisory-database/blob/3d0187a2ae2380c20a24da45e4f13e8bdd980484/vulns/open-webui/PYSEC-2026-2716.yaml","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/SSVC/data/2025/CVE-2025-46719.json","https://github.com/stevologic/security-recipes.ai/blob/f6129ff19f955337f9f194ea8d5a3937dce9acb8/content/recipes/cve/cve-2025-46719-open-webui-vulnerable-to-stored-xss-via-unescaped-markdown-token-in-markdowntokens-svelte-leading-to-full-acco.md","https://github.com/cyberdudebivash/cyberdudebivash-blog/blob/be80f241080dc6ff384600eeed4a5579a42f2524/api/intel/products/cve-2025-46719-pip-open-webui.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2025/POC-AVE-2025-0006.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0006.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0005","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-46571","title":"Open WebUI 存储型跨站脚本漏洞","description":"Open WebUI（自托管AI平台）存在存储型跨站脚本（Stored XSS）漏洞，CWE-79分类。低权限用户可通过`/api/v1/files/`接口上传包含恶意JavaScript代码的HTML文件，服务器返回文件ID后，攻击者可构造链接诱导管理员点击，从而劫持管理员账户，进而利用管理员权限通过平台功能实现远程代码执行。默认配置下低权限用户上传的文件仅管理员或上传者自身可查看，限制了攻击面但未消除风险。该漏洞影响0.6.6之前版本，CVSS评分5.3，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.3,"aliases":["CVE-2025-46571","GHSA-8gh5-qqh8-hq3x"],"sources":["ghsa"],"published":"2025-05-05T19:15:57.050","updated":"2026-06-17T09:26:38.630","remediation":"升级 Open WebUI 至 v0.6.6 及以上版本（官方已修复文件上传 XSS 漏洞）。如暂无法升级，可在反向代理层限制 `/api/v1/files/` 端点的上传文件类型，禁止上传 `.html` 后缀文件作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/open-webui/open-webui/blob/main/backend/open_webui/routers/files.py#L434-L438","https://github.com/open-webui/open-webui/commit/ef2aeb7c0eb976bac759e59ac359c94a5b8dc7e0","https://github.com/open-webui/open-webui/security/advisories/GHSA-8gh5-qqh8-hq3x"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2025/POC-AVE-2025-0005.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0012","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0012.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-2070","title":"联想 FileZ 客户端不当XML解析任意文件读取漏洞","description":"联想 FileZ（联想网盘）客户端存在 XML 外部实体（XXE）解析不当漏洞（CWE-611）。本地低权限用户若访问攻击者构造的恶意 URL，客户端在解析相关 XML 时可能被诱导读取系统任意文件，造成敏感信息泄露。攻击需本地条件并依赖用户交互（访问特制链接），不影响完整性与可用性。受影响版本为 FileZ Client 11.0.0.10 之前，CVSS 约 5.0–5.1（中危）。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-2025-2070"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-04-25T16:15:26.180","updated":"2026-06-17T09:06:14.800","remediation":"立即将联想网盘 FileZ 客户端升级至 11.0.0.10 或更高版本以修复不当 XML 解析（XXE）问题。升级前请从官方渠道下载安装包并关闭正在运行的 FileZ 客户端。若暂时无法升级，应避免打开未知或不可信链接，限制低权限本地用户访问 FileZ，并在企业环境中通过应用管控禁止运行受影响旧版本客户端作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.filez.com/securityPolicy/2.html?1744703100","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/431324351d69005e5e9ea9d116dc965ce92ed482/cves/2025/2xxx/CVE-2025-2070.json","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-20701.md","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/94ba69fdac5ced9eb8795ce09aa042cbb168d31b/2025/2xxx/CVE-2025-2070.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/c2672e36893bd220d6f65c955e260796d11ed64b/2025/CVE-2025-20700.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2025-2070.md","https://github.com/adysec/hwpoc/blob/e2c3d33b7e2870449a687c9b1cfa4c48990c946b/docs/2025/%E8%81%94%E6%83%B3_%E8%81%94%E6%83%B3%E7%BD%91%E7%9B%98filez-cve-2025-2070-%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96.toml","https://github.com/Hashmire/cpeApplicabilityGeneratorPages/blob/4588dccb1f913705444975eb2a5eb79962bf2513/generated_pages/CVE-2025-2070.html","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc48b6c04c59ceff2d71da45cd843fc1d449dc48/SSVC/data/2025/CVE-2025-2070.json","https://github.com/auracast-research/race-toolkit/blob/eec737d3cef3f6155c513c05eddadb07ee8e9197/README.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2025/04/GHSA-58xr-825m-v3pq/GHSA-58xr-825m-v3pq.json","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-2070"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0012.toml"}]